key = os.path.join(self.test_folder, self.temp_file_name)
bucket = self.test_bucket
temp_file = self._test_file()
assert self.s3.file_exists(bucket, key) is False
assert self.s3.file_upload(temp_file, bucket, self.test_folder) == key
assert self.s3.file_exists(bucket, key) is True
assert self.s3.file_contents(bucket, key) == self.temp_file_contents
assert self.s3.file_delete(bucket, key) is True
assert self.s3.file_exists(bucket, key) is False
os.remove(temp_file)
